  "title": "Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Looking for staff in Yishun and Boon Keng/Bendemeer region.</p><p><br /></p><p>We are a GP clinic looking for permanent full-time clinic assistants who are caring, willing to learn, and passionate about the job.</p><p><br />Nursing background / previous clinic experience not required</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Main responsibilities:</strong><br />- Answer phone calls and attend to patients' inquiries<br />- Registering and collecting payment<br />- Dispensing of medications<br />- Assist doctor in clinical procedures<br />- Basic clinic housekeeping<br />- Maintain day-to-day operations of the clinic</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Skills / Education required</strong><br />- Basic IT skill<br />- Would be given skill upgrading opportunity by going for company sponsored courses including but not limited to ECG, nebulisation, dressing, phlebotomy</p>",
